---
title: Lamb, Bacon & Leek Shepherd's Pie with Garlic Mash Topping
description: Let’s try our hand at the classic shepherd’s pie, filled with saucy lamb and veggies like cosy leek. It’s a comfort dinner that just gets comfier when a fluffy potato mash is spread on top to create the top of the pie. We’ve reached peak cosiness now!
